"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"A handy list (cross posted from [here](https://womeninfilm.kitsplit.com/resources)). \\n\\n* **[Coaching for Women in Film]() —** a program I started at KitSplit that offers free coaching sessions for women in TV&Film, by women in TV&Film. \\n* **[Digital Women Leaders](https://www.digitalwomenleaders.com/)**—free coaching resource geared towards journalists, including visual journalists\\n* **[New York Women in Film & Television](http://www.nywift.org/default.aspx)**, as the name suggests, offers [scholarships and funding](http://www.nywift.org/article.aspx?id=FUNDING)primarily to women in NYC, but the resources it has regarding the [status of female filmmaker](http://www.nywift.org/article.aspx?id=STAT)s apply to all. Check out their [Nancy Malone Intern/Mentor program](https://www.nywift.org/intern-program/) (for early career filmmakers). NYWIFT is a parter and early supporter of KitSplit :)\\n* **[Glassbreaker Films](https://glassbreakerfilms.org/)** develops grants and programs to support female filmmakers working on nonfiction stories.\\n* **Women In Film [Mentoring Program](https://womeninfilm.org/mentoring-circles/)**—for Los Angeles filmmakers who are active members of Women in Film\\n* **[Women in Media events](https://womennmedia.com/events/)**—for Los Angeles & NY filmmakers, LA-based Women in Media has a variety of events, some geared towards mentorship\\n* **[Women in the Arts and Media Coalition](http://www.womenartsmediacoalition.org/)** sends out newsletters with job opportunities for women involved in video making. [Subscribe here](http://www.womenartsmediacoalition.org/opportunities).\\n* **[WomenArts](http://www.womenarts.org/)**, in addition to featuring [how-tos for creators](http://www.womenarts.org/skills/index/), offers a list of [organizations that provide emergency funds](http://www.womenarts.org/funding-resources/emergencyfunds/) for artists who are struggling to pay rent, medical expenses, or to otherwise meet their needs due to circumstances beyond their control.\\n* **[Her Film Project](http://www.herfilmproject.com/festivals.html)** contains a terrific list of international festivals aimed at cultivating diverse talent.\\n* **[Wellwood Woman](http://wellywoodwoman.blogspot.com/)** was started by Marian Evans, who compiles comprehensive lists of [competitions and awards](http://wellywoodwoman.blogspot.com/p/competitions-awards-funding.html), and an amazing [page of international activist sites](http://wellywoodwoman.blogspot.com/p/activist.html) related women in video, film, and media.\\n* **[Film Fatales](http://www.filmfatales.org/)** is a networking group for female filmmakers with chapters in NYC and LA. You can apply to join on their site.\\n* **[Chicken and Egg](http://chickeneggpics.org/)** develops programs and provides grants to female non-fiction filmmakers. Read about their [open calls and fellowship process](http://chickeneggpics.org/programs/).\\n\\n   \\n \",\"timestamp\":1640132489,\"title\":\"Resources for Women in Film & Video\\n\"},\"digest\":\"W4vP3vgjXBqfPVnlRLg5EZlPU5S1WLk5XOS0zS9xz-U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x573DA9f782bea0EA6fc00218f2F345A73a2D8b10\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6QCsVn3sTIJoRj6UPeDJTGeljqfHzeTGSt3MS9VlXbQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FqS1240gl5WSJt_sfSeUhEAGYHelxAJPk5r3Q3tWHD8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"gIKp9C6gO0b84jgkPaRVOKTrvr-nYhjGxPj6FpVvkXbisBStNz754kMDRypd9KyMZlVzOlqsTHz_-Ui9CvC4rw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb39975c10767cb7f6a08eb6285bce1568fd0de8012cf05178dafd8d1de2a0ca71aa0092f5499d004d65e922d0d4b1c66bc05f03fc0bfd8e0a0d2be160e9f86781b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6QCsVn3sTIJoRj6UPeDJTGeljqfHzeTGSt3MS9VlXbQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FqS1240gl5WSJt_sfSeUhEAGYHelxAJPk5r3Q3tWHD8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"W4vP3vgjXBqfPVnlRLg5EZlPU5S1WLk5XOS0zS9xz-U\"}"